\title{Relaxed Control}
\date{2026-03-10}
\author{boat}
\taxon{Definition}
\import{math-lib}

\p{
Consider the [bolza problem](opt-6002) subject to #{\dot{\vx} (t) = f(t,\vx (t), \vu (t)),\ \vu (t) \in U}, where #{U} is a [compact](gtop-0008) [metric space](gtop-0009).
}

\p{
Relaxed controls replace the set #{U} by the space of [Radon probability measures](gtop-000N) on #{U}.
}
